<bibRefCitation author="Stephensen, K." box="[304,512,1559,1583]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36" pagination="57 - 237" refId="ref52943" refString="Stephensen, K. (1946) The Brachyura of the Iranian Gulf. Danish Scientific Investigations in Iran, Part IV. E. Munksgaard, Copenhagen, 57 - 237." type="book chapter" year="1946">Stephensen (1946)</bibRefCitation>
